    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Right now the widget doesn't recognize `_geoloc` as a special value to display geo search information, so that would be the minimum needed change.\n\nTo work around this there's the possibility to declare a fake facet attribute in the settings and change its value. That works well, and then the template idea works well, but it's very hacky :) \n",
